HEADWORD: partitioning
<hw>partitioning</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>An analysis into mutually
exclusive categories.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> breakdown.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Separation by the creation of a boundary that
divides or keeps apart.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> division, partition, segmentation,
subdivision.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>partitionist</ent>⟦br⟧
